		"name": "Meru Recruitment Portal API",
		"description": "# Meru County Recruitment Portal API\n\nThis collection contains all the API endpoints for the Meru County Recruitment Portal. \n\n## Base URL\n- **API Base URL**: `https://api.merucountypublicserviceboard.or.ke/api`\n- **Domain URL**: `https://api.merucountypublicserviceboard.or.ke` (for health checks)\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require a Bearer Token. To authenticate:\n1. Use the **Login** request in the **Authentication** folder.\n2. The `accessToken` and `refreshToken` will be automatically saved to collection variables.\n3. Subsequent requests will use the `{{accessToken}}` variable in their Authorization header.\n\n## Roles\n- **Applicant**: Standard user role for job seekers.\n- **Admin**: Staff role for managing vacancies, departments, and reviewing applications.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
